{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"808ffea7-4bed-49e2-ae53-c9fad0163934","content":"There's no pipeline file in the current directory, so here's the general migration guidance:\n\n### Replace `VSTest@3` with `dotnet test`\n\nMicrosoft.Testing.Platform (MTP) doesn't use `vstest.console.exe`, so **`VSTest@3` won't work**. Use a `script` or `DotNetCoreCLI@2` task instead:\n\n```yaml\n- task: DotNetCoreCLI@2\n  displayName: 'Run tests'\n  inputs:\n    command: test\n    projects: '**/*Tests.csproj'\n    arguments: >\n      --configuration Release\n      --logger \"trx;LogFileName=results.trx\"\n      --results-directory $(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults\n      --collect \"Code Coverage;Format=Cobertura\"\n```\n\n### Key changes\n\n1. **TRX reports** — pass `--logger \"trx\"` to `dotnet test`. MTP honours the same logger syntax.\n2. **Code coverage** — use `--collect \"Code Coverage;Format=Cobertura\"` (or your preferred collector). Works the same way.\n3. **Publish results** — since you're no longer using VSTest@3's built-in publishing, add explicit publish steps:\n\n```yaml\n- task: PublishTestResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish test results'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    testResultsFormat: VSTest\n    testResultsFiles: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/*.trx'\n\n- task: PublishCodeCoverageResults@2\n  displayName: 'Publish code coverage'\n  condition: always()\n  inputs:\n    summaryFileLocation: '$(Agent.TempDirectory)/TestResults/**/coverage.cobertura.xml'\n```\n\n### Project-side prerequisites\n\nIn each test `.csproj`, ensure MTP is enabled:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n### Summary\n\n| Concern | VSTest@3 (old) | MTP (new) |\n|---|---|---|\n| Test runner | `vstest.console` | `dotnet test` / built-in |\n| TRX output | Built-in | `--logger \"trx\"` |\n| Coverage | Built-in | `--collect \"Code Coverage\"` |\n| Publish results | Automatic | `PublishTestResults@2` |\n| Publish coverage | Automatic | `PublishCodeCoverageResults@2` |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"56ed03fb-529e-4a17-9762-022049e0f407","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"There are no pipeline files in the repository. The user is asking a general guidance question about migrating from VSTest@3 to Microsoft.Testing.Platform in Azure DevOps CI pipelines. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":684,"requestId":"7031:39211A:DB3CE3C:F17534D:69F2A815"},"id":"59e36a0b-794a-411c-a7b2-c66f75f860a9","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:53:54.624Z","parentId":"ea6457af-3d62-49f6-a176-19db4ff33c58"}
